 and importance of the shear and of the anisotropic stresses.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Feb 2013 18:41:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 6 Mar 2013 19:00:55 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 7 Mar 2013 16:01:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-15"}
