adient due to weak line smearing. For 3-annuli bins, a minimum S/N\nof ~ 5 on the [NII] line is required for the faintest annulus to constrain the\ngradients with meaningful errors.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Feb 2013 21:00:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-15"}
