s are then a natural consequence of the accretion of\nsatellites.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Feb 2013 21:00:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 18 Sep 2013 19:00:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-15"}
