ynamical systems and simply exposing\nglobal properties of static and cosmological solutions, including horizons,\nsingularities, etc. For analytic approximations we also propose an integral\nequation well suited for iterations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Feb 2013 09:48:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 12 Apr 2013 15:11:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-15"}
