 order logic on trees extended\nwith predicates for equality and disequality between subtrees, and cardinality.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Feb 2013 12:52:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 1 Apr 2013 09:29:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-07-01"}
